snippet.title: Putrefaction Trailer
snippet.description:
Putrefaction is an OldSchool FPS game, with tons of weapons, enemies and gore, made by just one guy. This is a Steam Greenlight trailer for the game.
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=441501212 Vote if you want to see this game in Greenlight!
